transcripts:
GAB: Hello, I'm Gabin from the Slow-Mo guys. Tide recently challenged us to ruin a brand new lab coat. Obviously , I made Dan wear it. I don't want that kinda mess on me. 

DAN: Look at this. It is almost too bright for my eyes!

GAB: Yeah. Now enjoy the cleanliness for a moment. Have you  enjoyed it?

DAN: Yeah.

GAB: Now we're gonna get it real dirty. See if we can wash it out. We messed it up really good. Alright Dan do you have your goggles on? 

DAN: Yup my body is ready.

GAB: Excellent. here we go. I blasted him with ketchup.

DAN: That was really direct actually.

GAB: That is lovely. I hit him with chocolate pudding. Nailed it! I can't believe it knocked your googles off. And I hit him with mint chocolate chip ice cream. Directly in the face! You just turned to a completely different color. Oh man! Man that is gross. Made an absolute dog's dinner for lab coat. Well, not it's up to Tide to get this lab coat clean. 

DAN: Yeah they got their workout.

GAB: They do indeed.
